#: ../../source/minutes/minutes-2025.rst:198
msgid ""
"Co-Treas: controversy over the Olympiad; school numbers are small to "
"participate, which has made removal."
msgstr ""
"Co-Treas: controverse over de Olympiade; het aantal scholen dat meedoet is "
"klein, waardoor verwijdering heeft plaatsgevonden."

#: ../../source/minutes/minutes-2025.rst:200
msgid ""
"Incoming-Chair: Will coordinate with LOCNOC about what is really happening, "
"maybe include NAEIC about inclusion"
msgstr ""
"Inkomend-voorzitter: Zal afstemmen met LOCNOC over wat er echt gebeurt, "
"misschien NAEIC erbij betrekken over opname"

#: ../../source/minutes/minutes-2025.rst:202
msgid "Member: New NWO curriculum includes astronomy in physics"
msgstr "Lid: Nieuw NWO-curriculum omvat astronomie bij natuurkunde"

#: ../../source/minutes/minutes-2025.rst:204
msgid "Treas.: We welcome input from members"
msgstr "Treas: We verwelkomen input van leden"

#: ../../source/minutes/minutes-2025.rst:206
msgid "Member: NNV could also advertise it"
msgstr "Lid: NNV zou er ook reclame voor kunnen maken"

#: ../../source/minutes/minutes-2025.rst:208
msgid ""
"Incoming-Chair: Discussion has been not to just abolish, so should be "
"rekindled, and maybe have new directions."
msgstr ""
"Inkomend-voorzitter: Discussie is geweest om niet zomaar af te schaffen, dus"
" moet nieuw leven worden ingeblazen en misschien nieuwe richtingen worden "
"ingeslagen."

#: ../../source/minutes/minutes-2025.rst:210
msgid ""
"Member: asks and BM-SDeR replies there is still a Belgian astronomy Olympiad"
msgstr ""
"Lid: vraagt en BM-SDeR antwoordt dat er nog steeds een Belgische "
"astronomieolympiade is"

#: ../../source/minutes/minutes-2025.rst:212
msgid ""
"Member: What are the costs of the Exec office, treas. Replies these are "
"structural"
msgstr ""
